paleio

paleio is a collaboration chat. with file sharing. and invitations. and syntax highlight. and image preview.

works with (at least):
- chrome 18
- safari 5
- firefox 11

main dependencies:
- rvm with ruby 1.9.2-p290
- rails 3.2.2
- postgresql 9.1
- redis 2.x
- devise 2.0.4
- eventmachine em-websocket 0.3.6
- bluepill 0.6.0
- requirejs
- backbone 0.9.1
- bootstrap 2.0.1

check INSTALL for a fast setup in Oracle VirtualBox.

